## Team Lead Responsibilities

### frontend_architect
- Review all frontend tasks
- Ensure design system compliance
- Coordinate between frontend sub-agents
- Validate component architecture

### backend_architect
- Review all backend tasks
- Ensure API contract compliance
- Coordinate database and service work
- Validate performance and security

### ai_systems_architect
- Review all AI tasks
- Ensure Vertex AI best practices
- Coordinate AI agent development
- Validate conversation flows

### qa_strategy_lead
- Review all quality tasks
- Ensure test coverage
- Coordinate regression testing
- Validate release readiness

### devops_platform_lead
- Review all deployment tasks
- Ensure CI/CD pipeline integrity
- Coordinate Cloud Run deployments
- Validate infrastructure changes

---

## Escalation Path

1. **Agent → Team Lead**: Technical decisions, blockers
2. **Team Lead → Project Lead**: Cross-team dependencies, resource conflicts
3. **Project Lead → User**: Strategic decisions, scope changes
